<h1>Time Stamps in UK Government Systems</h1>
<pre class="metadata">
Group: Tech & Data Standards
Status: Draft Guidance Document
</pre>
<section>
  <h2>Time Stamps Guidance</h2>
Where RFC3339 is sufficient for a given set of requirements, then it's
advisable to use it alone (not full ISO 8601) to maintain simplicity.
</section>
